name: Vickie Dooley
description: I am a very intelligent & honest woman I’m very Self Confident, Responsible, Friendly, Romantic, Spontaneous,down to earth, Easygoing, Sophisticated, Open-Minded, Earthy, Simple, Loving, Intellectual, Serious, Humorous, Sensitive,also God fearing woman….I basically would just like to meet a good hearted man with strong morals, values and character.I love the ocean and try to at least get there for vacation every year. I enjoy fishing, not that I have any real success, but I can bait my own hook. I love comedy, especially live stand up.. laughing is the best feeling.
